{"tid":1331434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者欲申請庇護，台灣建議「不可帶口罩」沖擊才能獲批","createTime":"2019-07-19T02:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T03:14:28.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"66b07784fae4da399001e515dc50f486b46440e1","tid":1331434,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:42:11.000Z","msg":"香港反送中浪潮持續，其中 7 月 1 日大批示威者衝擊立法會，據《自由亞洲電台》報導，7.1 衝擊後有十多名香港示威者到台灣，正接觸台灣陸委會希望尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n報道指從多個官方和非官方消息渠道證實，十多名香港示威者已抵達台灣。一名不願透露姓名的台灣律師正協助這些示威者，他相信這批人要申請延長居留台灣，技術上會有困難，因為他們未被香港警方拘捕或檢控，而且他們當時都帶了口罩，無法向台灣方面證明他們衝擊過立法會。<br />\n      報道又引述陸委會回覆查詢指，台灣支持香港民主自由及保障人權，根據香港澳門關係條例等法規，香港居民到台灣無論是停留或居留都有規定，至於因為政治因素令安全自由受威脅的香港居民，亦會提供必需的協助。陸委會又表示，如果台灣政府收到申請個案，會在尊重人權保障與人道關懷原則下，考慮相關法規妥善處理。"},{"pid":"11962c9a298c03f490dbb7b87fc8f3193ee64871","tid":1331434,"uid":6845,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">起樓主底<br />\n篇野根本唔係呢個意思</span>"},{"pid":"8571fe5271b429004407dd5db1c4e89f177f4f33","tid":1331434,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ompeGQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FompeGQX.png&h=21f02728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴了口罩<br />\nWho know"},{"pid":"b49d6d9bb458725e4fc9637e4d4d07e687d78b32","tid":1331434,"uid":39777,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11962c9a298c03f490dbb7b87fc8f3193ee64871","tid":1331434,"uid":6845,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">起樓主底<br />\n篇野根本唔係呢個意思</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"好耐無見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7f08e30ce1ef466beb88fdf8f0e57b836887ce","tid":1331434,"uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"11962c9a298c03f490dbb7b87fc8f3193ee64871","tid":1331434,"uid":6845,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">起樓主底<br />\n篇野根本唔係呢個意思</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"事實姐，戴左口罩搵鬼信你要庇護"},{"pid":"519ed55024625f8a82daa99472efb58f26431a6b","tid":1331434,"uid":3659,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:47:54.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0916eac0555e7934780c70f09174bd4d1ea9e8","tid":1331434,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"離罩"},{"pid":"0a48ab69ada0ffd90a712b85c7482e9a834cbf49","tid":1331434,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"而且他們當時都帶了口罩，無法向台灣方面證明他們衝擊過立法會。"},{"pid":"5c42f46af4d9922aeb436e5fd4a46629fcbe1142","tid":1331434,"uid":64981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"台灣律師：戴口罩難證明衝擊<br />\n<br />\n樓主spin：台灣建議唔好戴口罩衝擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fb0abb45bee85c7d444a538f98b29cdea7c6cf","tid":1331434,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c42f46af4d9922aeb436e5fd4a46629fcbe1142","tid":1331434,"uid":64981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"台灣律師：戴口罩難證明衝擊<br />\n<br />\n樓主spin：台灣建議唔好戴口罩衝擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"再講一次<br />\n善用起底功能"},{"pid":"366f87f0b9509c3589839907c4e52c92ae534f2c","tid":1331434,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:53:56.000Z","msg":"起底<br />\n負評<br />\n上一頁<br />\n<br />\n唔好再推"},{"pid":"5170e937e6f818fe399afb0925ae3e7c